<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<title>用户信息</title>
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
	<meta name="keywords" content="">
	<meta name="description" content="">
	<meta name="author" content="chenxiaoyong@ehaier.com">
	<meta name="application-name" content="TS APP">
	<meta content="yes" name="apple-touch-fullscreen">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, email=no">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/public.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages/recommend.css">
</head>
<body class="userProfile-page">
	<!-- 头部导航  -->
	
	<div class="nav">
		<div class="nav__inner clearfix">
			<div class="nav__back"></div>
			<div class="nav__title">意见反馈</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 热线电话 -->
	<div class="customer-service">
		购买和售后支持，请拨打24小时客服电话<br>
		<a href="tel:4006999999">4006-999-999</a>
	</div>
	<div class="feedback-form">
		<p>海尔顺逛微小店相关内容，请填写下表：</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<label>反馈类型：</label>
				<span class="select-box">
					<select id="sType">
						<option value="-1">请选择</option>
						<option value="0">功能意见</option>
						<option value="1">界面意见</option>
						<option value="2">您的新需求</option>
						<option value="3">操作意见</option>
						<option value="4">流量问题</option>
						<option value="5">其他</option>
					</select>
				</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<label>反馈内容：</label>
				<textarea id="content"></textarea>
			</li>
			<li>
				<label>联系方式：</label>
				<input type="number" id="mobile"/>
			</li>	
		</ul>
	</div>
	<a href="javascript:;" class="btn btn-large feedbackBtn" id="submitBtn">提交</a>

</body>
</html>
